        <h2 class="pane-title">
      For Service Providers    </h2>
    
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <p>We offer many resources to health and community service providers across Manitoba. </p><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf"><a href="/service-providers/our-services" title="">Our Services</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/resource-library" title="">Resource Library</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/service-providers/translation-services">Translation Services</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/projects">Projects &amp; Reports</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/research">Research &amp; Evaluation</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/service-providers/educators-and-schools">Educators &amp; Schools</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="/service-providers/safer-sex-supplies">Safer Sex Supplies</a></li></ul>  </div>

  
